  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Full Stack Developer (AI & Video Analytics)",
  "description": "<p>We are partnering with a leading AI and Edge Computing firm delivering actionable video insights for Smart Cities, Retail, and Security. If you have what it takes for this role, we'd love to speak with you!</p><h3>The Role</h3><ul><li><p>Own product enhancements and new deployments, participating in the full lifecycle from ideation to production.</p></li><li><p>Develop front-end and back-end components with a focus on localization (i10n), OWASP security standards, and accessibility (WCAG).</p></li><li><p>Design and develop REST APIs and API-centric microservices.</p></li><li><p>Implement data protection, build testing pipelines in Git, and manage deployments from Docker Hub across stage and production environments.</p></li></ul><h3>Technical Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>2–3 years in Application Development.</p></li><li><p>Core Stack: .NET Core (C#), Angular, and MySQL.</p></li><li><p>Backend/Scripting: Proficiency in Python; knowledge of Node.js or JavaScript is a plus.</p></li><li><p>Cloud & Infrastructure: Hands-on experience with AWS/Azure, Virtual Machines, and Docker/Kubernetes container management.</p></li><li><p>Committed to \"Clean Code,\" software architecture principles, and maintainable version control.</p></li></ul><h3>Why Join Us?</h3><ul><li><p>Work on AI solutions serving both government and private global enterprises.</p></li><li><p>Collaborative, open-communication environment, no rigid hierarchies.</p></li><li><p>Performance-based remuneration and clear opportunities for professional development.</p></li></ul>",
